## UX & Accessibility

Follow the comprehensive guidelines in `AGENTS.md` at the project root. Key non-negotiables:

- Full keyboard support per WAI-ARIA APG. Visible focus rings via `:focus-visible`.
- Hit targets ≥ 24px (≥ 44px mobile). Mobile inputs ≥ 16px font-size.
- Honor `prefers-reduced-motion`. Animate only `transform` and `opacity`.
- URL reflects app state. Links use `<a>` / `<Link>`, never `<div onClick>`.
- Skeletons mirror final layout. No dead ends. Design empty/error/dense states.
- Dark mode: `color-scheme: dark` on `<html>`, explicit colors on native elements.
- Prefer native semantics over ARIA. Accessible names on all interactive elements.
